ance and destiny, from Wong Kar-Wai and David Lynch to films such as Serendipity and Sliding doors.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aMotion picture producers and directors. 4aFilm and Media Studies 2019. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aAmants du Pont-Neuf.  aCahiers du Cinéma.  aHyères festival.  aLeos Carax.  aPierre or The Ambiguities.  aPola X.  aStrangulation Blues.  aautistebavarde.  ametaphorical usage.  apersonal mythology.  astudent film.  averisimilitude.1 aDaly, Fergus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDowd, Garin, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aDowd, Garin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagez978311128363040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152614159040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526141590423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526141590/original  a978-3-11-128363-0  Manchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagec1986d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles